#: ../../source/docs/development-environment/BT/tb.rst:2 4413db12046440abb88a3765078b6648
msgid "泰凌微TB系列"
msgstr "Telink TB Series"

#: ../../source/docs/development-environment/BT/tb.rst:6 4225b906acba4daaae6a02abc281cf85
msgid "1. 简介"
msgstr "1. Introduction"

#: ../../source/docs/development-environment/BT/tb.rst:7 d73a958c64254639a28256e2feef94d0
msgid "安信可科技针对物联网设计通用型的蓝牙模组，其功能强大、用途广泛。可以用于智能灯、智能插座、智能空调等其他智能家电。同时符合BLE 5.0及SIG Mesh规范，可直接通过智能手机组建Mesh网络，也可对接天猫精灵智能音箱，适用于多种智能家居应用场景。"
msgstr "Ai-Thinker Technology has designed a general-purpose Bluetooth module for IoT applications. It is powerful and widely applicable, and can be used in smart lights, smart sockets, smart air conditioners, and other smart home appliances. It also complies with BLE 5.0 and SIG Mesh specifications. A Mesh network can be created directly via a smartphone, and it can also be connected to Tmall Genie smart speakers, making it suitable for various smart home application scenarios."

#: ../../source/docs/development-environment/BT/tb.rst:9 b7a9434a33fa445abe976613dceda62a
msgid "更多资料请转跳： `安信可官方docs <https://docs.ai-thinker.com/blue_tooth>`__"
msgstr "For more information, please visit: `Ai-Thinker official docs <https://docs.ai-thinker.com/blue_tooth>`__"

