msgid "先通过查看是否依附，再看看是否在列表中？ **2条指令即可！** ::"
msgstr "First check whether the device is attached, and then check whether it appears in the device list.  **Only two commands are needed.** ::"

#: ../../source/docs/development-environment/BT/tb.rst:105 521bc4c1fe7b41e5ada3d61fd5410ae4
msgid "3.2 权限问题 /dev/ttyUSB0"
msgstr "3.2 Permission Issue: /dev/ttyUSB0"

#: ../../source/docs/development-environment/BT/tb.rst:106 f811245c65904ebb8193e7e085070049
msgid "**使用某些 Linux 版本向 TB-02 烧写固件时，可能会出现 Failed to open port /dev/ttyUSB0 错误消息。此时，可以将当前用户增加至 :ref: `Linux Dialout 组 <linux-dialout-group>`。**"
msgstr "**When flashing firmware to the TB-02 using some Linux versions, the error message \"Failed to open port /dev/ttyUSB0\" may appear. In this case, you can add the current user to the: `Linux Dialout Group <linux-dialout-group>`.**"

#: ../../source/docs/development-environment/BT/tb.rst:108 e2534f276fa5468e9bfe33109ea32971
msgid "因为默认情况下，只有root用户和属于dialout组的用户会有读写权限，因此直接把自己的用户加入到dialout组就可以了。操作完命令后要重启一下，就永久生效了。 ::"
msgstr "By default, only the root user and users belonging to the dialout group have read and write permissions. Therefore, you can simply add your user account to the dialout group. After running the command, restart the system, and the change will take effect permanently. ::"
